Directions: Take Mike Padgett South to Goshen Rd. Turn right. Turn left on Goshen Lake Dr. Home is on right.
Property Description: Here is a wonderful opportunity to own a cute home with a nice layout in beautiful Augusta! This home sits on a lot directly behind a peaceful golf course. The backyard is privacy fenced and has a nice covered patio. The living room features a fireplace, and the spacious kitchen has plenty of cabinets. The large owner bedroom suite features a dual vanity bathroom and walk-in closet! This home is conveniently located to the Goshen Plantation Golf Course, major roads, and industrial areas.

Directions: Take exit 5 towards Edgefield (US HWY 25), go past Murphey's Village, Stephens Mill subdivision will be on the left. Take the second right onto Stephens Mill Drive, then first left onto Stephens Mill Ct. House it strait ahead.
Property Description: Beautiful home located on .62 acre lot. Kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors, and custom tile back splash. Great floor plan with hardwood floors in the main living areas. Large living room with fireplace and vaulted ceiling. Master bedroom features walk-in closet. In the backyard you will find a large deck perfect for entertaining.

Directions: North Belair Road-- To Evanston Drive.  Left onto Dry Creek Road.
Property Description: Look no further!  This brick ranch style home has been completely updated and is ready for new owner.  Kitchen has tiled flooring; new appliances; and eat-in breakfast area.  Laundry room off kitchen with built-ins.  Formal dining area, spacious great room with masonry fireplace.  Added feature includes 12x15 heated sun room.  Ceiling fans in all bedrooms.  Updated baths.  Large master suite with walk-in closet.  Rocking chair front porch overlooking lushly landscaped front yard.  Rear yard is fenced, flat and perfect for children, dogs and gardening.  Perfect in every way!  Newly listed and affordably priced.  Evans School district.
